&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class="section-num"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt; &lt;a href="#h:38aae4aa-a802-4cff-9ffb-1ecebc230218" rel=""&gt;Lock out user after three failed login attempts&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
